genresAdvancedInfo.name: igbo trap
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Igbo trap is a fusion of traditional Igbo music from Nigeria with the modern trap sound popularized in the United States. The genre combines traditional Igbo rhythms and instruments with heavy basslines, trap drums, and auto-tuned vocals. The result is a unique blend of African and American music that has gained popularity in Nigeria and beyond.
